00:33:20.130 --> 00:33:22.750
OK, so here's the design.

00:33:22.750 --> 00:33:24.840
So here's what these guys
did, this wonderful lab

00:33:24.840 --> 00:33:25.440
in Australia.

00:33:25.440 --> 00:33:26.220
I love this stuff.

00:33:26.220 --> 00:33:28.680
OK, so they trained
