00:48:07.850 --> 00:48:09.120
That was the early claim.

00:48:09.120 --> 00:48:09.620
OK.

00:48:12.380 --> 00:48:15.800
And for further, the claim
implicit in this article

00:48:15.800 --> 00:48:17.810
in this figure is
